<Base
  title="ChatGPT vs Perplexity vs Google AI: Where Can You Get Cited First?"
  description="Perplexity is the fastest engine to crack (live retrieval, visible citations), Google AI rewards existing search equity, and ChatGPT is the slowest but stickiest. The source mix of each engine and the order to attack them."
